This paper discusses the potential impact of artificial intelligence on humanity and the need for a "Friendly AI" to safeguard human values. This topic is most closely related to the field of AI (cs.AI), as well as robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY) which are also concerned with the development and control of intelligent systems. The paper also touches on ethical considerations, which could fall under the category of computational complexity (cs.CC) or machine learning (cs.LG) which often deal with ethical and fairness issues in algorithmic decision-making.
